{"tid":2226893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵有錢仔/搵“好歸宿”嘅你，入一入黎","createTime":"2020-10-02T10:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T16:10:20.000Z","uid":120847,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0ee42b6e5c97e034537e57568c9f6ba90dd6e0","tid":2226893,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"想嫁個有錢人，無非因為你想有安全感，想有倚靠<br />\n<br />\n可能你日做夜做好撚受氣好辛苦<br />\n但其實我想講，嫁個有錢人，其實可能同打另一份工冇分別，呢份工仲要24/7咁OT冇放工冇年假<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要靠男人開飯，你嘅老闆其實就變左你老公咁解<br />\n係佢有錢而你冇錢呢個地位不平等嘅情況下，你就唯有不停取悅佢服從佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日啲錢唔係你自己嘅，一日都冇必然架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一係就做騙子咁厄夠錢就走人，做唔到呢點，就唔好抱住嫁個有錢人嘅心態去做女人，你唔會得到想要嘅人生架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed2d9f42a480d3ecfd1aab82a5e4dfc8fc58188","tid":2226893,"uid":262698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T10:49:23.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔會聽"},{"pid":"2cca95c2cefaec1fc174cabdcf7b95ccef19a3d3","tid":2226893,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b54770943a8ce6cc7c2a7e29f376c192745cbee","tid":2226893,"uid":367814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}